data.description: Adorable one-story home in the heart of Huntsville, Located close to the SHSU campus. With Scott Johnson Elementary and Huntsville Intermediate School nearby, it's a convenient location for families with school-going children. Open cabinets above the counters being installed suggests a modern and open feel in the kitchen, providing additional storage space. Call for a showing today.
